https://github.com/d80b2t/VHzQ/tree/master/data/WSA_VSA



 Purpose
====================================================================
This gives the salient details to quickly access the WFCAM Science
Archive (WSA) and the VISTA Science Archive (VSA) in order to obtain
the near-infrared ZYJHK photometry for the VHzQ sample.





 WSA_VSA_LOGINS
====================================================================
Gives the details for how to login into the WSA and VSA.


 TABLE_DESCRIPTIONS
====================================================================
Gives further details on the various databased Tables that are most
relevant in the WSA and VSA.


 SAMPLE_SQL_QUERIES
====================================================================
Gives a set of example SQL queries that can be used to garner
information from the WSA and VSA.

 BestWSA_VSA_magnitudes.csv
 is the result of running the
 "Select best magnitude in each band for each QSO".








